    public class StatistiquesListActivity
extends HarmonyFragmentActivity
implements HarmonyListFragment.OnClickCallback, HarmonyListFragment.OnLoadCallback
    This class will display Statistiques entities in a list. This activity has a different behaviour wether you're on a tablet or a phone. - On a phone, you will have a Statistiques list. A click on an item will get you to StatistiquesShowActivity. - On a tablet, the StatistiquesShowFragment will be displayed right next to the list.
